What you need to know:

Phoenix has won four straight games, all on the road, to improve on the league's best record of 34-9.In Los Angeles, LeBron James scored 25 points as the Los Angeles Lakers ended a three-game losing skid with a 101-95 win over the Utah Jazz.The Lakers rebounded for Monday night's win after an embarrassing 37-point loss to the Denver Nuggets on Saturday.